message.body: Happy birthday!!!!!!!!!!!! The big 2-4! Not that it feels any different from any other year! I hope it's a good one and that that Michael boy planned something amazing! Love you!!!!

Haha. Thank you! He made two reservations so that I could choose and both fell through. One turned out to be in Jersey. He didn't check the address. And the other changed their menu so they don't have what I wanted. Haha. So I have to think of something. But he tried.
Awww. It is the thought that counts!!! We'll either way, have a fantastic day!!!!
Any idea what you'd want to do for your bday?

Haha. I haven't gotten that far yet. I have to think about what I want to do for today first. But nothing big. Probably just dinner. A regular hang out. I just want to relax before I start work on Monday.
I hear ya! That's fine! Haha. Do what you gotta do!
